OL,4,CLoot boxes linked to problem gambling
OL,5,Cin new research
OL,6, The link between gaming loot boxes and
OL,7, problem gambling has been "robustly
OL,8, verified", according to a new report.
OL,10,FThe report, carried out by researchers
OL,11,Fat the universities of Plymouth and
OL,12,FWolverhampton, found that loot boxes
OL,13,F"are structurally and psychologically
OL,14,Fakin to gambling".
OL,16,FIt also found that large numbers of
OL,17,Fchildren are opening loot boxes.
OL,19,FThe UK government is already
OL,20,Fconsidering whether gambling laws
OL,21,Fshould cover such loot boxes.
